<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>116</hymn_number>
<key>C</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Bawi Jesuh min a thlum ngaingai, A min chim ka dai bal lai lo, Bawi
 Jesuh min sung bik nih cun, Ka lunglawmhnak a tlinter.

[C1]
   &quot;Jesuh&quot; a min a thlum ko, &quot;Jesuh&quot; ni fa aa khat ko, Zungzal
   thangthat awk tlak min, Mithiang nih aupi cio u (mithiang nih au pi cio
   u).

[V2]
 Jesuh min kha ka duh ngaingai, Ka ngaihchiat a hngalh i a phorh,
 Tihphan in a ka huhphenh ca'h, Bawi Jesuh min ka duh ko.

[C2]
   &quot;Jesuh&quot; a min a thlum ko, &quot;Jesuh&quot; ni fa aa khat ko, Zungzal
   thangthat awk tlak min, Mithiang nih aupi cio u (mithiang nih au pi cio
   u).

[V3]
 Ka lung a lawmhter zungzal ca'h, A min theih ka dai bal lai lo, A
 thawngin ka mitthli a hul, Jesuh min hlorh cio ko u.

[C3]
   &quot;Jesuh&quot; a min a thlum ko, &quot;Jesuh&quot; ni fa aa khat ko, Zungzal
   thangthat awk tlak min, Mithiang nih aupi cio u (mithiang nih au pi cio
   u).

[V4]
 Ka dawtmi Jesuh minthlum cu, Bia in an chim kho bal lai lo. A
 thangthat karh chin awk caah, Jesuh min thangthat cio u.

[C4]
   &quot;Jesuh&quot; a min a thlum ko, &quot;Jesuh&quot; ni fa aa khat ko, Zungzal
   thangthat awk tlak min, Mithiang nih aupi cio u (mithiang nih au pi cio
   u).</lyrics>
<title>JESUH MIN CH116</title>
</song>